FBIS4-8468 "dreeu072_b_94002" FBIS-EEU-94-072 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 BULGARIA Paris Club Talks `Ended With Complete Success' Paris Club Talks `Ended With Complete Success' AU1404071494 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 0500 GMT 14 Apr 94 AU1404071494 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network Bulgarian BFN [Text] I would first like to remind our listeners that we are awaiting confirmation of a piece of news that we received from a source close to the Government Commission on the foreign debt negotiations, namely that late last night, at 0130 in the French capital, the talks with the Paris Club of official creditors ended with complete success. According to the same source, an formula was agreed for rescheduling repayments of the debt for 11 years, with a seven-year gratis period.
